Admins can access the Request Log Detail page by clicking the [Logs] button corresponding to an instance on the Monitoring page. This page displays the general information section (challenge id) and the text-based log content area. Users can click [Refresh] to update the latest logs without reloading the entire page, or use the auto-refresh function to automatically update after a period of time; the system simultaneously displays the latest refresh time to ensure transparency and trackability.
