TB-01	Admin	Admin MVC	External-to-Admin Boundary	HTTPS requests from privileged users into the admin system.
TB-02	Contestant	Contestant Portal	External-to-User Boundary	HTTPS requests from contestants into the competition interface.
TB-03	Internet	Challenge Gateway	Public-to-Exploit Boundary	Exploit traffic from the Internet directed to the proxy that routes to challenge environments.
TB-04	Admin MVC	NFS Server	AdminMVC -to-Storage Boundary	Flow for storing challenge files and other security-related files.
